    </poem>
    <poem name="flurry" id="flurry-098" seq="098" date="2015-08-21" time="19:20" year="2015" index="" xml:space="preserve">
      <stanza>
        <line>Flurry…</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>there is beauty in the wallowing,</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>but necessary to come out of it with heart open</line>
        <line>seeing all sides,</line>
        <line>all things,</line>
        <line>all scenarios,</line>
        <line>appreciate all inside the self</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>chaotic streams of living</line>
        <line>… a life full of heart in love with all</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>“… gold and mud,</line>
        <line>happiness and pain,</line>
        <line>the laughter of childhood</line>
        <line>and the apprehension of death.” (Herman Hesse)</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>flurries of snowflakes in August</line>
        <line>came down to cool the ground</line>
      </stanza>
    </poem>
    <poem name="pure happy suffering" id="pure-happy-suffering-099" seq="099" date="2015-08-21" time="21:12" year="2015" index="" xml:space="preserve">
      <stanza>
        <line>impermanence is joyful</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>pure suffering is beautiful because it is always there</line>
        <line>  - in various forms</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>do not dilute it with numbness artificial escapes</line>
        <line>(can’t since 04 - NO point to turn back to - ever)</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>strength coming from emptiness invading all directions</line>
        <line>in A W E</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>strength coming from absolute DISASSOCIATED compassion</line>
        <line>NOT fucking empathy - you don’t get it dearest mummy</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>strength coming from passing through gate less gates feeling shore waves in your face blistering blue sand emerald green horses running wild splashing sound of tornado invisible currents shock torrents dark undercutting oceans and Earth globes beyond</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>strength coming from within the core of the sub atomic presence</line>
        <line>the purple quantum fields up side down and negative spin</line>
        <line>the extension of myriads of nothing waves nothing movements nothing minds</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>fields of complete nothing buildings washed walls adobe stone the Spanish brought into our lands, strange creatures, strange sounds, green magnetic blood, ultra everything</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>no not thinking not-thinking arising appearances with time into space and back from graves and cremation ashes power herbs of ancient lands, Anasazi</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>beaches of nothing cities mirage blinding flash silver sunrise</line>
        <line>sphinx leaving post to disappear into maze of yawn laid out</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>cyclops eating water to empty oceans still seeing no tide</line>
        <line>expression of nothingness in eyes seeing far back in time</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>breaches in chains of command and evidence all break down order is exposed as criminal futility in language and subtle corruption walls hollow as rain filled drums fall</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>the white lands of light inside compressed nuclei inside fusion of star fuel born out of extraordinary different foreign fleets of cascading accelerating nothing illuminated empty fields</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>at the edge there is a peculiar pattern repeating sound vinyl pressure</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>—</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>‘I’ realize 'I am’ in darkness bliss</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>not what I thought</line>
        <line>all the worn out phrases are bullshit</line>
        <line>not what I mean</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>another level after all lives are run out</line>
        <line>imposing order is just not an option</line>
        <line>it crashed 111111 years ago when they arrived</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>not what I</line>
        <line>all phrases are dead</line>
        <line>not what</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>DISOWN this whole notion of ‘reality’; as it is completely hollow; and fragile</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>bliss beyond beyond the senses</line>
        <line>there is another angle</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>crying now, as the forms are dead</line>
        <line>birth and death are dead</line>
        <line>emptiness is dead</line>
        <line>.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>next universe comes next moment</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>with all the white yellow flowers</line>
        <line>on her black dress,</line>
        <line>that she wanted to throw away,</line>
        <line>but I kept insisting,</line>
        <line>so pretty</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>a picture one day</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>the blueish pearl bracelet causing her to smile inside</line>
        <line>the beaches of missing my being</line>
        <line>the presence I never seen before in human form</line>
        <line>the focus and precision</line>
        <line>the happy and light voice</line>
        <line>touching my heart</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>deeply wordless moment forever</line>
        <line>.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>next universe comes next moment</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>deep core</line>
        <line>deep vast</line>
        <line>deep hyper</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>this is contradiction</line>
        <line>short breath</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>primordial extra terrestrial source inside us</line>
        <line>the mind gate opens yet to realize</line>
        <line>alayavijnana</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>before blood</line>
        <line>before sensing</line>
        <line>before blink</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>realmless dhyana</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>staying as that doesn’t belong</line>
        <line>staying as I don’t belong</line>
        <line>anymore</line>
        <line>anywhere</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>as</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>I don’t believe</line>
        <line>I don’t express</line>
        <line>I don’t have any opinion</line>
        <line>I don’t have any knowledge</line>
        <line>I don’t have any experience</line>
        <line>I don’t have any space</line>
        <line>I don’t have any mind</line>
        <line>I don’t have any thing</line>
        <line>I don’t have any body</line>
        <line>I don’t have any</line>
        <line>I don’t have any structure</line>
        <line>I don’t have any construct</line>
        <line>I don’t have any concept</line>
        <line>I don’t have any protocol</line>
        <line>I don’t have any control</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>as I don’t</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>have any past</line>
        <line>have any present</line>
        <line>have any future</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>I am</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>freed from freedom</line>
        <line>freed from prison</line>
        <line>freed from form</line>
        <line>freed from birth</line>
        <line>freed from death</line>
        <line>ultimately free</line>
        <line>.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>next universe comes next moment</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>the hot breeze</line>
        <line>sun set</line>
        <line>corn field, moving</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>as she walks beneath the old oaks</line>
        <line>as we put the wet towels to dry</line>
        <line>weighed down</line>
        <line>to not move</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>no people</line>
        <line>as we play in the playground</line>
        <line>too fast silly dizzy</line>
        <line>happy and light</line>
        <line>touching my heart</line>
        <line>deeply wordless moment forever</line>
        <line>.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>next universe comes next moment</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>worldly distractions and terms</line>
        <line>why can’t we just leave that behind</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza>
        <line>simply Love and breathe</line>
        <line>go for it</line>
        <line>as is?</line>
      </stanza>
    </poem>
    <poem name="pure happy suffering edit" id="pure-happy-suffering-edit-099" seq="099" date="2015-08-26" time="20:31" year="2015" index="" xml:space="preserve">
